
shortcut for del key to change to empty type

how it works:
    Automaticlaly loads ../../images/map.json
    saves in ./map.json.
        save function only updates currently loaded level. If changes made in another level, they wont be applied
    map.json needs to be manually copied to ../../images
    run "make" in images
    run "make" in src



change type on right click (type should include "empty")
    either we lock the choice to tiles that are already in level or we need to update the palettes if we add new blocks

remove objects and badguys
move objects or badguys
add objects and badguys (will affect palette if adding those that are not in map already
add blocks (will affect palette if adding those that are not in map already

    


